Package: plot3d
Type: Package
Title: This package only contains a function to generate an animation of an RGL 3D plot.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Placido Pellegriti
Maintainer: Placido Pellegriti <placidopellegriti@live.it>
Description: Having the three axes data a three dimensional spinning plot gets generated.
Points can have different colours based on the cluster they are in, and different shape
if they are misclassified instances. This packeges is based on the following packages:
  rgl https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/rgl/index.html
  magick https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/magick/index.html
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
